<p>
  Makes the channel secret. Secret channels do not appear in the channel list (/list) for non-members and are hidden from /whois output. Mutually exclusive with +p (private).
</p>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_terminal}>Usage</.help_h4>
<pre>/mode +s    — Make channel secret
/mode -s    — Remove secret mode</pre>
<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>See Also</.help_h4>
<p><.help_link topic="mode-p">Private (+p)</.help_link></p>
